      <title>Instagramas</title>
      <link>https://www.natansantolo.com/post/instagramas/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Apr 2016 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://www.natansantolo.com/post/instagramas/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://www.natansantolo.com/assets/images/instagramas/instagramas.png&#34; alt=&#34;Instagramas&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I built this simple component for &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.marcelaviola.com.ar&#34;&gt;Marcela&amp;rsquo;s Website&lt;/a&gt;, the idea is to show the latest pictures you&amp;rsquo;ve published in your Instagram.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I tried to make it flexible by adding a few configurations, you can choose the type of render, amount of images, also some flags to hide tags and favorites. &lt;a href=&#34;http://natos.github.io/instagramas/&#34;&gt;See all the possible configurations and examples&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&#34;gallery&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;instagramas&#34; data-count=&#34;4&#34; data-show-tags=&#34;true&#34; data-show-likes=&#34;true&#34; data-access-token=&#34;13931722.44ad315.9e06216e9b454e19b048e5e335051691&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;script async src=&#34;https://www.natansantolo.com/assets/js/instagramas.min.js&#34;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;


&lt;p&gt;I also made a &lt;a href=&#34;http://natos.github.io/instagramas/&#34;&gt;test page&lt;/a&gt; where you can find &lt;a href=&#34;http://natos.github.io/instagramas/&#34;&gt;more example implementations&lt;/a&gt; and some notes about styling. Also if you like to hack things go and &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/natos/instagramas&#34;&gt;grab the code in github&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;ll keep improving this little project, its quite fun and there&amp;rsquo;s quite a lot of opportunities. As soon as I make some time, the first thing I want to fix is the CSS implementation and documentation.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Last example, here is my last Instagram:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&#34;gallery&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;instagramas&#34; data-count=&#34;1&#34; data-show-tags=&#34;true&#34; data-show-likes=&#34;true&#34; data-render-type=&#34;standard_resolution&#34; data-access-token=&#34;13931722.44ad315.9e06216e9b454e19b048e5e335051691&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;script async src=&#34;https://www.natansantolo.com/assets/js/instagramas.min.js&#34;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;


&lt;p&gt;I hope you find this useful :)&lt;/p&gt;
